Titolo: Age of Empires III: Definitive Edition

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Age of Empires III: Definitive Edition is a real-time strategy video game developed by  Tantalus Media and Forgotten Empires and published by Xbox Game Studios. It is a remaster of the original game Age of Empires III, celebrating the 15th anniversary of the original. It features significantly improved visuals, a remastered soundtrack, two new game modes, and two new civilizations. It includes all previous expansions from the original game. It was released on October 15, 2020.